If you are verified on ROBLOX you should receive a yellow shield next to your name. If you aren't verified it will tell you that you aren't. How do I verify My government ID to ROBLOX? https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/4407282410644-Age-ID-Verification This website will let your know the requirements in order to be verified on ROBLOX. NOTE This does not guarantee that a person is a safe and non-scamming trader, This just lets you know that they have been verified on ROBLOX. Happy Trading!
